---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---


<Layout title="Cylinder Liner Kit - PT Pilarindo Jaya Abadi" >

    <div class="bg-white mt-20">

        <main class="mx-auto px-4 pb-24 pt-14 sm:px-6 sm:pb-32 sm:pt-16 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
            <!-- Product -->
            <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-7 lg:grid-rows-1 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-10 xl:gap-x-16">
                <!-- Product image -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-4 lg:row-end-1">
                    <div class="aspect-h-3 aspect-w-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
                        <img src="product-1.jpg"
                             alt="Cylinder Liner Marine Engine Sparepart"
                             class="object-cover object-center bg-repeat">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Product details -->
                <div class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-2xl sm:mt-16 lg:col-span-3 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-end-2 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none">
                    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl">
                                Cylinder Liner Kit (Marine Engine)
                            </h1>

                            <h2 id="information-heading" class="sr-only">Informasi Produk</h2>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Kategori: Engine Parts (Yanmar / Daihatsu / MAN)
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-500">
                        Komponen vital untuk ruang bakar mesin induk kapal Anda. Dibuat dari material <i>Centrifugal Cast Iron</i> berkualitas tinggi yang tahan terhadap gesekan ekstrem dan suhu tinggi, memastikan kompresi mesin tetap optimal dan umur pemakaian yang panjang. Tersedia untuk berbagai model mesin utama (Main Engine) dan bantu (Auxiliary).
                    </p>

                    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-4 sm:grid-cols-1">
                        <button type="button"
                                class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-black bg-black px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2">
                            Minta Penawaran Harga
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Keunggulan Utama</h3>
                        <div class="prose prose-sm mt-4 text-gray-500">

                            <ul role="list" class="space-y-6">
                                <li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
                                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6">
                                        <div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-900 ring-1 ring-gray-300"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500"><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Material Premium</span> Tahan aus & korosi air laut.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
                                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6">
                                        <div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-900 ring-1 ring-gray-300"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500"><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Presisi Tinggi</span> Standar toleransi OEM Jepang.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
                                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6">
                                        <div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-900 ring-1 ring-gray-300"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500"><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Sertifikasi Class</span> BKI / Lloyds Register available.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-900 ring-1 ring-gray-300"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500"><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Garansi</span> 12 Bulan atau 5000 Jam Operasi.</p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Spesifikasi Teknis</h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                            Tersedia untuk bore size 180mm hingga 450mm. Paket penjualan termasuk O-Ring Seal Kit tahan panas (Viton) dan sertifikat pengujian material (Mill Test Certificate).
                        </p>
                    </div>


                </div>

                <div class="mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-2xl lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none">
                    <div>
                        <div class="border-b border-gray-200">
                            <div class="-mb-px flex space-x-8" aria-orientation="horizontal" role="tablist">
                                <button id="tab-faq"
                                        class="border-transparent text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-800 whitespace-nowrap border-b-2 py-6 text-sm font-medium"
                                        aria-controls="tab-panel-faq" role="tab" type="button">FAQ Produk
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div id="tab-panel-faq" class="text-sm text-gray-500" aria-labelledby="tab-faq" role="tabpanel"
                             tabindex="0">
                            <h3 class="sr-only">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

                            <dl>
                                <dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">Apakah liner ini sudah di-honing?</dt>
                                <dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
                                    <p>
                                        Ya, semua cylinder liner yang kami suplai sudah melalui proses <i>plateau honing</i> untuk memastikan pelumasan oli yang optimal dan mengurangi gesekan awal saat <i>break-in period</i>.
                                    </p>
                                </dd>
                                <dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">Merek mesin apa saja yang kompatibel?</dt>
                                <dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
                                    <p>
                                        Kami memiliki stok siap kirim untuk Yanmar (seri M200, M220, T240), Daihatsu (seri DK-20, DK-28), Hanshin, dan Akasaka. Untuk merek Eropa seperti Wartsila atau MAN, mohon hubungi sales untuk cek stok indent.
                                    </p>
                                </dd>
                                <dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">Bagaimana dengan pengiriman?</dt>
                                <dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
                                    <p>
                                        Item ini termasuk <i>heavy cargo</i>. Kami menggunakan peti kayu standar ekspor (ISPM 15) untuk pengiriman aman ke seluruh pelabuhan dan galangan kapal di Indonesia.
                                    </p>
                                </dd>

                            </dl>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </main>


    </div>


</Layout>
